"}, "24372": {"changesets": [{"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010601 - Avoid losing track of primary frame in nsSubDocumentFrame::Init. r=layout-reviewers,dshin a=dmeehan\n\nWhen we're replicating a fixed-positioned frame that happens to contain a\nsubdocument, we were losing track of the primary frame of the element.\n\nThe regressing bug made us rely a bit more in the frame tree structure\nhere (of FindContainerFrame() and such), but this was a pre-existing bug.\n\nThis prevents us from clobbering it and is enough to fix the crash and restore\npre-regression behavior, so it is the minimal thing to uplift.\n\nFurther clean-ups incoming.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279297\n", "files": ["layout/generic/nsSubDocumentFrame.cpp"], "git_node": "68393ec8d807cc435e3173098ba5a9215e680281", "git_parents": ["0224fece2422ced85d58569bb601a9959b4a52cc"], "node": "998562bcd5d5ed7a51ca225e2611c65edc20d152", "parents": ["f023f03b0bdd8378b58e27ad8078c070a44664e0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010601 - Deal with not being the primary subdoc frame in some cases. r=layout-reviewers,dshin a=dmeehan\n\nIt's very sketchy to propagate state from non-primary frames to the\nframeloader.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279298\n", "files": ["layout/generic/nsSubDocumentFrame.cpp"], "git_node": "ae3b1d02644df425bcb511399038fd1a97731b08", "git_parents": ["68393ec8d807cc435e3173098ba5a9215e680281"], "node": "c95e7f50d46d31a3e5f0938313352380a50ebfe1", "parents": ["998562bcd5d5ed7a51ca225e2611c65edc20d152"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010608 - Null-check view transition named element in MatchClassList. r=view-transitions-reviewers,nical a=dmeehan\n\nKeep the debug assert, in case we find a repro...\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279177\n", "files": ["dom/view-transitions/ViewTransition.cpp"], "git_node": "686d1054deda472f12496d6081c0351d3b7d9f59", "git_parents": ["ae3b1d02644df425bcb511399038fd1a97731b08"], "node": "bd889c82c7fdbb49960875c8836b79eb695dcaca", "parents": ["c95e7f50d46d31a3e5f0938313352380a50ebfe1"], "tags": []}, {"author": "iorgamgabriel \u003ciorgamgabriel@yahoo.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010764 - Fix  [@ java.lang.IllegalStateException: at androidx.fragment.app.Fragment.getParentFragmentManager(Fragment.java) ]. r=android-reviewers,Roger a=dmeehan\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279267\n", "files": ["mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/prompts/src/main/java/mozilla/components/feature/prompts/dialog/TimePickerDialogFragment.kt"], "git_node": "fa7443add4bea670fb47fd492c66775a661bd823", "git_parents": ["686d1054deda472f12496d6081c0351d3b7d9f59"], "node": "d9b7709b71f05149b2976fadaf93da339ae358f9", "parents": ["bd889c82c7fdbb49960875c8836b79eb695dcaca"], "tags": []}], "date": 1768748797, "git_changesets": ["68393ec8d807cc435e3173098ba5a9215e680281", "ae3b1d02644df425bcb511399038fd1a97731b08", "686d1054deda472f12496d6081c0351d3b7d9f59", "fa7443add4bea670fb47fd492c66775a661bd823"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24373": {"changesets": [{"author": "Release Engineering Landoscript \u003crelease+landoscript@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No Bug - Import translations from main\n", "files": ["mobile/android/android-components/components/compose/awesomebar/src/main/res/values-cs/strings.xml", "mobile/android/android-components/components/compose/awesomebar/src/main/res/values-hu/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-cs/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-hu/strings.xml"], "git_node": "8789d16fd92750a45132d61e5f81fcea6081457e", "git_parents": ["fa7443add4bea670f