ttps://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279541\n", "files": ["browser/components/ipprotection/IPPVPNAddonHelper.sys.mjs", "browser/components/ipprotection/IPProtectionHelpers.sys.mjs", "browser/components/ipprotection/IPProtectionService.sys.mjs", "browser/components/ipprotection/docs/Components.rst", "browser/components/ipprotection/moz.build", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/browser/browser_IPProtectionService.js"], "git_node": "5021e4a840786763dcef8c3b61e73c3b2c5bf556", "git_parents": ["efccc847a999809437373605c3eaea1be3d9377f"], "node": "f034754114a0d5c7d503fa2270e5dcb44e552c1b", "parents": ["c7d62ac50ef076cffc99c4a872420d57092fab26"], "tags": []}], "date": 1768838352, "git_changesets": ["5021e4a840786763dcef8c3b61e73c3b2c5bf556"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24384": {"changesets": [{"author": "Delia Pop \u003cdpop@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1868289 - Fix intermittent deleteDownloadsOnQuitTest UI test  a=dmeehan DONTBUILD\n\nThe #deleteDownloadsOnQuitTest UI test was flaky when attempting to verify the download prompt: in the previous implementation, if the assertion failed, a fallback method allowed for the test to try downloading the file again.\nDue to bad timing, an overlap between the download prompt and a different \u201cDownload file again?\u201d prompt could, causing the test to fail.\n\nTo avoid this potential issue I made the following changes:\n1. I\u2019ve added an explicit waitForExists to make sure the download prompt exists\n2. I\u2019ve removed the retry loop, but used better locators using resource IDs to better assert the download prompt elements.\n3. I\u2019ve added a 1s wait right after clicking the download link for better syncronization\n\nThe UI test successfully passed 50x on Firebase. [[ https://treeherder.mozilla.org/jobs?repo=try&landoCommitID=172931  | Link ]]\nThe related UI tests that use the modified methods successfully passed 10x on Firebase. [[ https://treeherder.mozilla.org/jobs?repo=try&landoCommitID=173158 | Link ]]\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279254\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279499\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/androidTest/java/org/mozilla/fenix/ui/robots/BrowserRobot.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/androidTest/java/org/mozilla/fenix/ui/robots/DownloadRobot.kt"], "git_node": "d3d8d99f5218393d32536fdcd9150b9a9fba811e", "git_parents": ["5021e4a840786763dcef8c3b61e73c3b2c5bf556"], "node": "552e8a50d05adbbe3a2c5640240814407293d826", "parents": ["f034754114a0d5c7d503fa2270e5dcb44e552c1b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1768838484, "git_changesets": ["d3d8d99f5218393d32536fdcd9150b9a9fba811e"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24385": {"changesets": [{"author": "ffxbld \u003cffxbld@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No Bug, mozilla-beta repo-update HSTS HPKP remote-settings tld-suffixes ct-logs -  a=dmeehan\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279504\n", "files": ["netwerk/dns/effective_tld_names.dat", "security/ct/CTKnownLogs.h", "security/manager/ssl/StaticHPKPins.h", "security/manager/ssl/nsSTSPreloadList.inc", "security/manager/tools/log_list.json", "services/settings/dumps/blocklists/addons-bloomfilters.json", "services/settings/dumps/main/devtools-compatibility-browsers.json", "services/settings/dumps/security-state/intermediates.json"], "git_node": "fb4de7c16e00bd52b43740a764628dce5845e8d2", "git_parents": ["d3d8d99f5218393d32536fdcd9150b9a9fba811e"], "node": "4e55a4e0c3b4a323e4b9b9ba58765eddea65a3c8", "parents": ["552e8a50d05adbbe3a2c5640240814407293d826"], "tags": []}], "date": 1768838782, "git_changesets": ["fb4de7c16e00bd52b43740a764628dce5845e8d2"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24386": {"changesets": [{"author": "Dale Harvey \u003cdale@arandomurl.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010003 - Dont update trustpanel if not initialised.  a=dmeehan DONTBUILD\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.