d286697b711adcef123a6d7"], "tags": []}], "date": 1769619269, "git_changesets": ["bb9c8b5cd50d0652c54d307f60c628ddf95a5fdf"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24494": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jeff Boek \u003cjboek@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2003511 - Cancel loading bookmarks if weve navigated from the Bookmarks Fragment  a=dmeehan DONTBUILD\n\n[try](https://treeherder.mozilla.org/jobs?repo=try&landoCommitID=174243)\n\nPull request: https://github.com/mozilla-firefox/firefox/pull/34\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280766\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/bookmarks/BookmarkFragment.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/bookmarks/BookmarksMiddleware.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/bookmarks/EditBookmarkFragment.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/test/java/org/mozilla/fenix/bookmarks/BookmarksMiddlewareTest.kt"], "git_node": "8e3066987b6177d8e589815f523e16622947af2e", "git_parents": ["bb9c8b5cd50d0652c54d307f60c628ddf95a5fdf"], "node": "280945aeb7751e91e37e1b83d9f0fdda4433ef45", "parents": ["dd44a7c0365362d0f23d133ba0b3c28dbdec0562"], "tags": []}], "date": 1769619508, "git_changesets": ["8e3066987b6177d8e589815f523e16622947af2e"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24495": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jon Coppeard \u003cjcoppeard@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2011069 - Wait for any background sweeping to finish before marking gray bits invalid r=jandem a=dmeehan\n\nMarking gray bits invalid iterates the symbol arenas but this list can also be\nmodified by backgroun sweeping. The patch waits for any background sweeping to\nfinish first. Marking gray bits invalid only happens when background sweeping\nis running in response to OOM so this is not a problem.\n\nI tried adding an assert to catch this but it turns out it's not\nstraightforward to do this.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279831\n", "files": ["js/src/gc/GC.cpp"], "git_node": "dc95979596a825337479fa73421882663af83314", "git_parents": ["8e3066987b6177d8e589815f523e16622947af2e"], "node": "da7f963c060bd8a2180ffbfaffc60b31feb338a9", "parents": ["280945aeb7751e91e37e1b83d9f0fdda4433ef45"], "tags": []}], "date": 1769620010, "git_changesets": ["dc95979596a825337479fa73421882663af83314"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24496": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mark Striemer \u003cmstriemer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1997198 - Part 1: Wrap setting-groups in moz-cards  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D275335\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280794\n", "files": ["browser/components/preferences/widgets/setting-group/setting-group.mjs", "browser/components/preferences/widgets/setting-pane/setting-pane.mjs"], "git_node": "bd44969b169b93c31c27c88df3134930bfb47a69", "git_parents": ["dc95979596a825337479fa73421882663af83314"], "node": "148ed2b369e6ef31851dd4d177329de50e3ede2e", "parents": ["da7f963c060bd8a2180ffbfaffc60b31feb338a9"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mark Striemer \u003cmstriemer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1997198 - Part 2: Trim leading on moz-fieldsets with headings  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D275336\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280795\n", "files": ["toolkit/content/widgets/moz-fieldset/moz-fieldset.css", "toolkit/content/widgets/moz-fieldset/moz-fieldset.mjs", "toolkit/themes/shared/design-system/src/text-and-typography.css"], "git_node": "a03a17f9dd67927e3c20b621397199fc19994883", "git_parents": ["bd44969b169b93c31c27c88df3134930bfb47a69"], "node": "9ea897e23a3d856ea6d56c8d2a62b95c36a11e2b", "parents": ["148ed2b369e6ef31851dd4d177329de50e3ede2e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "mark \u003cmkennedy@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1969475 - Update moz-select to support menu separators for Applications section  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D278863\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280796\n", "files": ["toolkit/content/tests/widgets/test_moz_select.html", "toolkit/content/widgets/moz-select/moz-select.mjs", "toolkit/content/widgets/moz-select/moz-select.stories.mjs"], "git_node": "15e4c8588d6df542eb02f57694c82ccfc726d2ae", "git_parents": ["a03a17f9dd67927e3c20b621397199fc19994883"], "node": "a5873c2fa5e4a3ed582dd428861f887cfccba1fd", "parents": ["9ea897e23a3d856ea6d56c8d2a62b95c36a11e2b"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mark Striemer \u003cmstriemer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2005799 - Part 1: Settings to manage on-device AI features  a=dmeehan\n\nProvide settings to manage the Translations, PDF.js alt text,\nSmart Tab Groups, and Link Preview Key Points features.\n\nAvailable (default): UI is visible but requires confirmation. If the\nuser confirms in the feature the state will move to Enabled.\n\nEnabled (opt-in): UI is visible, the feature can run, models will\ndownload on use as needed.\n\nBlocked: UI is hidden, downloaded models will be removed when moving to\nthis state.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D277063\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280797\n", "files": ["browser/components/preferences/OnDeviceModelManager.mjs", "browser/components/preferences/config/aiFeatures.mjs", "browser/components/preferences/main.js", "browser/components/preferences/tests/browser_aiFeatures.js", "browser/themes/shared/preferences/preferences.css", "modules/libpref/init/all.js"], "git_node": "139197dc57d63861f261ecc9216e22903a1e7730", "git_parents": ["15e4c8588d6df542eb02f57694c82ccfc726d2ae"], "node": "112cf1c1aeaea4bdbe4f4c73d59def05723fd29a", "parents": ["a5873c2fa5e4a3ed582dd428861f887cfccba1fd"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mark Striemer \u003cmstriemer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2005799 - Part 2: Remove debug on-device AI section  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279746\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280798\n", "files": ["browser/components/preferences/config/aiFeatures.mjs", "browser/components/preferences/preferences.js", "browser/locales-preview/aiFeatures.ftl"], "git_node": "50b5ba561da4e4211d85170a975010aa380ed5fe", "git_parents": ["139197dc57d63861f261ecc9216e22903a1e7730"], "node": "1ce0bc69dec06b7037aae0071ab8f2db32931988", "parents": ["112cf1c1aeaea4bdbe4f4c73d59def05723fd29a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Beth Rennie \u003cbeth@brennie.ca\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2011286 - Collect all pref constants into a single object  a=dmeehan\n\nWe have a log of *_PREF constants floating around. Let's collect them\nall together into a single place, since we're about to add another one.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279577\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280799\n", "files": ["toolkit/components/nimbus/ExperimentAPI.sys.mjs"], "git_node": "8c50c0010120a6b1d9d021658b6de223468b09b8", "git_parents": ["50b5ba561da4e4211d85170a975010aa380ed5fe"], "node": "1cbf5d07d814343f694d8919a210da74e1facff2", "parents": ["1ce0bc69dec06b7037aae0071ab8f2db32931988"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Beth Rennie \u003cbeth@brennie.ca\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2011286 - Update recipes when the global AI control pref changes  a=dmeehan\n\nIf the user disables the global AI control, Nimbus needs to re-evaluate\nthe targeting of all enrollments.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279578\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280800\n", "files": ["toolkit/components/nimbus/ExperimentAPI.sys.mjs", "toolkit/components/nimbus/test/unit/head.js", "toolkit/components/nimbus/test/unit/test_RemoteSettingsExperimentLoader.js"], "git_node": "5f028e7b668e100b81c6692e51a9dd1b4ed24775", "git_parents": ["8c50c0010120a6b1d9d021658b6de223468b09b8"], "node": "75b28707baba05760256c799a7f49005ebad0bf3", "parents": ["1cbf5d07d814343f694d8919a210da74e1facff2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Beth Rennie \u003cbeth@brennie.ca\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2011286 - Re-render Firefox Labs when Nimbus finishes updating enrollments  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279579\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280801\n", "files": ["browser/components/preferences/experimental.js", "browser/components/preferences/tests/browser_experimental_features_filter.js"], "git_node": "7f372d45f6b0b9247e171f0e0e52e17792fb571e", "git_parents": ["5f028e7b668e100b81c6692e51a9dd1b4ed24775"], "node": "8fbfd15118c2aee6e4817f4b3541108ccbd38bd9", "parents": ["75b28707baba05760256c799a7f49005ebad0bf3"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Beth Rennie \u003cbeth@brennie.ca\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2011286 - Record browser.ai.control.default in Nimbus targeting context ping  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280113\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280802\n", "files": ["toolkit/components/nimbus/lib/TargetingContextRecorder.sys.mjs", "toolkit/components/nimbus/metrics.yaml"], "git_node": "a8b10eb2fb2a705858a41fcb077c06821a91c180", "git_parents": ["7f372d45f6b0b9247e171f0e0e52e17792fb571e"], "node": "d29902dd076e5a3c637a653d77dda232f6ac9f3f", "parents": ["8fbfd15118c2aee6e4817f4b3541108ccbd38bd9"], "tags": []}], "date": 1769632274, "git_changesets": ["bd44969b169b93c31c27c88df3134930bfb47a69", "a03a17f9dd67927e3c20b621397199fc19994883", "15e4c8588d6df542eb02f57694c82ccfc726d2ae", "139197dc57d63861f261ecc9216e22903a1e7730", "50b5ba561da4e4211d85170a975010aa380ed5fe", "8c50c0010120a6b1d9d021658b6de223468b09b8", "5f028e7b668e100b81c6692e51a9dd1b4ed24775"