rential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280768\n", "files": ["browser/components/newtab/AboutNewTabRedirector.sys.mjs", "browser/extensions/moz.configure", "browser/extensions/newtab/legacy-jar.mn", "browser/extensions/newtab/moz.build", "browser/extensions/newtab/test/xpcshell/head.js", "browser/installer/allowed-dupes.mn", "browser/modules/AboutNewTab.sys.mjs", "browser/moz.configure", "toolkit/modules/AppConstants.sys.mjs", "toolkit/modules/moz.build"], "git_node": "a595d70312778c561d386b8469c5e46379e347f9", "git_parents": ["dbf8f7244c3b9356e12b51e8748d2597a15c3aa5"], "node": "52a788080c5a1247ace20b7065f5ebeb659144cc", "parents": ["499db76c47ae5ffe79e389289f05cb90fb7537a8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike Conley \u003cmike@conley.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2009017 - Part 1: Block initializing ActivityStream on the newtabTrainhop Nimbus feature being ready.  a=dmeehan DONTBUILD\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279335\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280769\n", "files": ["browser/extensions/newtab/test/xpcshell/test_AboutHomeStartupCacheWorker.js", "browser/modules/AboutNewTab.sys.mjs"], "git_node": "2bb41f48f154c8125b8e41a02622f626560a4630", "git_parents": ["a595d70312778c561d386b8469c5e46379e347f9"], "node": "43c2b5c9fd316f457c6ac0383b4c9b22c19e225a", "parents": ["52a788080c5a1247ace20b7065f5ebeb659144cc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike Conley \u003cmike@conley.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2009017 - Part 2: Compute instant of profile creation and have ActivityStream cache it.  a=dmeehan DONTBUILD\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279336\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280770\n", "files": ["browser/components/newtab/test/browser/abouthomecache/browser_no_startup_actions.js", "browser/components/newtab/test/xpcshell/test_nimbus_newtabTrainhopAddon_onBrowserReady.js", "browser/extensions/newtab/lib/ActivityStream.sys.mjs", "browser/modules/AboutNewTab.sys.mjs", "testing/talos/talos/talos-powers/api.js"], "git_node": "2d61b9cd8a9334c74541ffd518fefa81a2c9b25c", "git_parents": ["2bb41f48f154c8125b8e41a02622f626560a4630"], "node": "352a7122761d4770e178f6568e42002889f66115", "parents": ["43c2b5c9fd316f457c6ac0383b4c9b22c19e225a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike Conley \u003cmike@conley.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2009017 - Part 3: Make StartupCacheInit feed start first amongst feeds.  a=dmeehan DONTBUILD\n\nThis is so that if there are any other feeds that want to emit actions on initialization\nthat the StartupCacheInit feed should hear about, it will be initialized and be able\nto hear about them.\n\nThis is needed for the PrefsFeed activation window check, which might emit actions on\ninitialization that a cached page should hear about.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279362\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280771\n", "files": ["browser/extensions/newtab/lib/ActivityStream.sys.mjs"], "git_node": "e01d57cd13c7b0a12f26bb409291a06703c272ce", "git_parents": ["2d61b9cd8a9334c74541ffd518fefa81a2c9b25c"], "node": "575336de33cde8686fec1bce3f737a6b774c825f", "parents": ["352a7122761d4770e178f6568e42002889f66115"], "tags": []}], "date": 1769693216, "git_changesets": ["a595d70312778c561d386b8469c5e46379e347f9", "2bb41f48f154c8125b8e41a02622f626560a4630", "2d61b9cd8a9334c74541ffd518fefa81a2c9b25c", "e01d57cd13c7b0a12f26bb409291a06703c272ce"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24500": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mike Conley \u003cmike@conley.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2012009 - Part 1: Don't retrieve scripts from non omni.ja JAR files from the ScriptPreloader or StartupCache.  a=dmeehan\n\nSystem add-ons can be installed in the profile directory as .xpi JAR files that\nare updated independently of the application. Prior to this patch, when these JARs\nare updated independently from the rest of the application, the ScriptPreloader\nand StartupCache can serve stale bytecode compiled from the previous version of\nthe JAR, causing the old code to execute even though the JAR has been replaced.\n\nThis fix here adds a helper to checking if a script's JAR file is in one of\nthe omni.ja files before using cached bytecode.\n\nScripts from the omni.ja files continue to benefit from bytecode caching as\nbefore.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280333\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280664\n", "files": ["dom/base/nsFrameMessageManager.cpp", "dom/xul/nsXULPrototypeCache.cpp", "js/xpconnect/loader/ScriptPreloader.cpp", "js/xpconnect/loader/mozJSModuleLoader.cpp", "js/xpconnect/loader/mozJSSubScriptLoader.cpp", "startupcache/StartupCacheUtils.cpp", "startupcache/StartupCacheUtils.h"], "git_node": "a58b53769446acb487efca89768dbf2105b55faf", "git_parents": ["e01d57cd13c7b0a12f26bb409291a06703c272ce"], "node": "53cb0c30f249ca5bae675729b4847887560e4180", "parents": ["575336de33cde8686fec1bce3f737a6b774c825f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike Conley \u003cmike@conley.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2012009 - Part 2: Add a regression test for ScriptPreloader.  a=dmeehan\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280334\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280763\n", "files": ["js/xpconnect/loader/ScriptPreloader.cpp", "js/xpconnect/loader/ScriptPreloader.h", "js/xpconnect/tests/marionette/manifest.toml", "js/xpconnect/tests/marionette/test_preloader_cache_bypass.py", "modules/libpref/init/StaticPrefList.yaml"], "git_node": "61f9d4f87fddd7284d951fa7f4c1afcd86331ca6", "git_parents": ["a58b53769446acb487efca89768dbf2105b55faf"], "node": "ecf1df381da34f7d866ec725193105fdaea03190", "parents": ["53cb0c30f249ca5bae675729b4847887560e4180"], "tags": []}], "date": 1769693267, "git_changesets": ["a58b53769446acb487efca89768dbf2105b55faf", "61f9d4f87fddd7284d951fa7f4c1afcd86331ca6"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24501": {"changesets": [{"author": "Byron Campen \u003cdocfaraday@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010657: Disable mDNS candidates when running outside of our CI  a=dmeehan DONTBUILD\n\nWe disable mDNS candidates when running in our CI already, so this makes\nthings consistent. This should reduce the flakiness of tests that do not\nobtain a capture permission.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279693\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280986\n", "files": ["testing/profiles/web-platform/user.js"], "git_node": "dc66e7ae8c1d35fa44ab80d339d7e3fcfd626d62", "git_parents": ["61f9d4f87fddd7284d951fa7f4c1afcd86331ca6"], "node": "c74f927196c2ee57ba892dfee062cf4aaf64941b", "parents": ["ecf1df381da34f7d866ec725193105fdaea03190"], "tags": []}], "date": 1769706599, "git_changesets": ["dc66e7ae8c1d35fa44ab80d339d7e3fcfd626d62"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24502": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mugurell \u003cMugurell@users.noreply.github.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010365 - Disable text autocorrect in the composable toolbar  a=dmeehan DONTBUILD\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280713\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280922\n", "files": ["mobile/android/android-components/components/compose/browser-toolbar/src/main/java/mozilla/components/compose/browser/toolbar/ui/InlineAutocompleteTextField.kt"], "git_node": "d2bc23882cca9059b468bd8e828e3d272f77f87d", "git_parents": ["dc66e7ae8c1d35fa44ab80d339d7e3fcfd626d62"], "node": "7421035c162ad91014ab2b6378d7b7749a628fd9", "parents": ["c74f927196c2ee57ba892dfee062cf4aaf64941b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1769706639, "git_changesets": ["d2bc23882cca9059b468bd8e828e3d272f77f87d"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24503": {"changesets": [{"author": "Rolf Rando \u003crrando@mozilla.com\u003e