rty.  a=dmeehan DONTBUILD\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280679\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D281078\n", "files": ["js/src/vm/Iteration.cpp"], "git_node": "c4df73ea91eaf3084f5ecee9ac1437779d389cc1", "git_parents": ["c431fc648253fba98567b076b175e237c2057688"], "node": "6bc9b9d3fa88dc420e789f77d2abdbbaad75f743", "parents": ["a87e24b6c5fa05e963bb8b42de05a9b8915da235"], "tags": []}], "date": 1769798539, "git_changesets": ["c4df73ea91eaf3084f5ecee9ac1437779d389cc1"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24524": {"changesets": [{"author": "Simon Farre \u003csfarre@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2001938 - Shortcut keys in combination with modifier should create UA  a=dmeehan DONTBUILD\n\nctrl+f5 which is used by google slides to go fullscreen is blocked\nbecause we don't consider keys bound to shortcuts that also is overriden\nby modifiers to be able to cause user gesture activation.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D274517\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D281189\n", "files": ["dom/base/test/useractivation/browser_useractivation_key_events.js", "dom/media/autoplay/test/mochitest/file_autoplay_policy_key_blacklist.html", "widget/TextEvents.h"], "git_node": "d7f916e01b2425d23212cf4f2741f496c6901b25", "git_parents": ["c4df73ea91eaf3084f5ecee9ac1437779d389cc1"], "node": "5ecefa2e254458a82341435fbb499a00970aec15", "parents": ["6bc9b9d3fa88dc420e789f77d2abdbbaad75f743"], "tags": []}], "date": 1769798605, "git_changesets": ["d7f916e01b2425d23212cf4f2741f496c6901b25"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24525": {"changesets": [{"author": "alin lastun \u003calastun@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010371 - Onboarding design update for small screen devices  a=dmeehan DONTBUILD\n\nUpdate the onboarding design for small-screen devices by changing the card layout from a floating card to a full-screen layout, while keeping the pagination dots visible to preserve navigation clarity\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D279635\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D281240\n", "files": ["mobile/android/android-components/components/compose/base/src/main/java/mozilla/components/compose/base/annotation/FlexibleWindowLightDarkPreview.kt", "mobile/android/android-components/components/compose/base/src/main/java/mozilla/components/compose/base/annotation/FlexibleWindowPreview.kt", "mobile/android/android-components/components/compose/base/src/main/java/mozilla/components/compose/base/annotation/FlexibleWindowPreviewSizes.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/onboarding/redesign/view/MarketingDataOnboardingPageRedesign.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/onboarding/redesign/view/OnboardingPageRedesign.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/onboarding/redesign/view/OnboardingScreenRedesign.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/onboarding/redesign/view/TermsOfServiceOnboardingPageRedesign.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/onboarding/redesign/view/ToolbarOnboardingPageRedesign.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/onboarding/view/OnboardingMapper.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/onboarding/view/OnboardingPageState.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/onboarding/view/OnboardingScreen.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/test/java/org/mozilla/fenix/onboarding/view/OnboardingMapperTest.kt"], "git_node": "73c025e2da006238fac29e3a3a8657de80703517", "git_parents": ["d7f916e01b2425d23212cf4f2741f496c6901b25"], "node": "44c4375d4023beca470f83419e4eefaeb93fbd18", "parents": ["5ecefa2e254458a82341435fbb499a00970aec15"], "tags": []}], "date": 1769798791, "git_changesets": ["73c025e2da006238fac29e3a3a8657de80703517"], "user": "dmeehan@mozilla.com"}, "24526": {"changesets": [{"author": "Erik Nordin \u003cenordin@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010993 - Ensure TranslationsEngine is destroyed when disabling Translations  a=dmeehan\n\nThis commit ensures that disabling the Translations feature will ensure\nthat the Translations Engine is destroyed. It also ensures that the engine\nactor is fetched every time, rather than relying on the cached value, which\nmay no longer be valid when re-enabling the feature.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280367\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D281207\n", "files": ["browser/components/translations/tests/browser/head.js", "toolkit/components/translations/TranslationsFeature.sys.mjs", "toolkit/components/translations/TranslationsUtils.mjs", "toolkit/components/translations/content/translations-engine.sys.mjs"], "git_node": "3161da8e7788f0025319cd043458d0eff9b0693b", "git_parents": ["73c025e2da006238fac29e3a3a8657de80703517"], "node": "f07b311b0fe41b57bda4e7f2a99991fceb2b0ecb", "parents": ["44c4375d4023beca470f83419e4eefaeb93fbd18"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Erik Nordin \u003cenordin@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010993 - Make about:translations react to feature enabledness  a=dmeehan\n\nThis commit ensures that the about:translations page reacts to the Translations\nfeature becoming disabled and enabled. When disabled, the page content should\nhide itself. When re-enabled, the page content should re-show and continue to\nwork as normal.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280368\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D281208\n", "files": ["toolkit/components/translations/actors/AboutTranslationsChild.sys.mjs", "toolkit/components/translations/actors/AboutTranslationsParent.sys.mjs", "toolkit/components/translations/actors/TranslationsParent.sys.mjs", "toolkit/components/translations/content/about-translations.mjs", "toolkit/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_about_translations_enabling.js", "toolkit/components/translations/tests/browser/shared-head.js", "toolkit/modules/ActorManagerParent.sys.mjs"], "git_node": "418dfd37f0ae6511b808adada17bb570bd886b2a", "git_parents": ["3161da8e7788f0025319cd043458d0eff9b0693b"], "node": "549f98f6a3de623ec6118464178119d15c7915cb", "parents": ["f07b311b0fe41b57bda4e7f2a99991fceb2b0ecb"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Erik Nordin \u003cenordin@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010993 - Make Translate QuickAction react to feature enabledness  a=dmeehan\n\nThis commit ensures that the Translate QuickAction is reactive to the\nenabled state of the Translations feature, which may now become disabled\nor re-enabled via the Settings UI.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280369\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D281209\n", "files": ["browser/components/urlbar/QuickActionsLoaderDefault.sys.mjs", "browser/components/urlbar/tests/browser/browser_quickactions_translate.js"], "git_node": "6251f65857c1f814c1513d58a3a2023c65933412", "git_parents": ["418dfd37f0ae6511b808adada17bb570bd886b2a"], "node": "331dd0c9cc7878181c520034ba074949afecda96", "parents": ["549f98f6a3de623ec6118464178119d15c7915cb"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Erik Nordin \u003cenordin@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010993 - Make SelectTranslations react to feature enabledness  a=dmeehan\n\nThis commit ensures that the SelectTranslations context menu item is reactive\nto the Translations feature becoming disabled or re-enabled, which may now\noccur in the Firefox Settings.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280370\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D281210\n", "files": ["browser/base/content/nsContextMenu.sys.mjs", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_select.toml", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_translations_select_ai_feature.js"], "git_node": "8071119264f232d7eef1b2bafd351898c2926d04", "git_parents": ["6251f65857c1f814c1513d58a3a2023c65933412"], "node": "831f26b2bd8c4423d2a4b93d012f4e48862cfee5", "parents": ["331dd0c9cc7878181c520034ba074949afecda96"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Erik Nordin \u003cenordin@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010993 - Make AppMenu react to Translations feature enabledness  a=dmeehan\n\nThis commit ensures that the \"Translate page...\" Application Menu Item correctly\nreacts to the Translations feature becoming enabled or disabled, which may now\noccur from the main Settings UI.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280371\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D281211\n", "files": ["browser/base/content/browser-init.js", "browser/base/content/browser.js", "browser/base/content/browser.js.globals", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_full.toml", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_translations_full_page_ai_feature_app_menu.js", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/head.js"], "git_node": "e06067c5bfdb02e1a0740defa0a550043fe25d38", "git_parents": ["8071119264f232d7eef1b2bafd351898c2926d04"], "node": "5ad1928058edf11f65b48408a6342cf6ef3054ba", "parents": ["831f26b2bd8c4423d2a4b93d012f4e48862cfee5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Erik Nordin \u003cenordin@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010993 - Rework StatePerTopChromeWindow to StatePerTab  a=dmeehan\n\nThis commit reworks our cached state from being per top chrome window\nto being truly per tab. Now that the feature can be disabled and enabled\nat runtime with multiple tabs open, there is more than just the current\ncontext that we may need to store in order to behave correctly if the\nfeature becomes re-enabled with multiple tabs still open.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280387\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D281212\n", "files": ["toolkit/components/translations/actors/TranslationsParent.sys.mjs"], "git_node": "21e00a1abeb89d6dfbeeb6cca0259f4d5a615cba", "git_parents": ["e06067c5bfdb02e1a0740defa0a550043fe25d38"], "node": "5ea175badcc0c6195ddb90c25ee9a19c70e5ba94", "parents": ["5ad1928058edf11f65b48408a6342cf6ef3054ba"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Erik Nordin \u003cenordin@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010993 - Make FullPage Translations react to feature enabledness  a=dmeehan\n\nThis commit ensures that the FullPage Translations functionality is able\nto react to the Translations feature becoming enabled and disabled, including\nmanaging the state of the Translations URL bar button across tabs, and handling\ncontext from tabs that may have been disabled mid translation.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280388\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D281213\n", "files": ["browser/base/content/browser-init.js", "browser/components/translations/content/fullPageTranslationsPanel.js", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_full.toml", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_translations_full_page_ai_feature_app_menu.js", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_translations_full_page_ai_feature_auto_translate.js", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_translations_full_page_ai_feature_mid_translation.js", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_translations_full_page_ai_feature_navigation.js", "browser/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_translations_full_page_ai_feature_urlbar_button.js", "toolkit/components/translations/actors/TranslationsChild.sys.mjs", "toolkit/components/translations/actors/TranslationsParent.sys.mjs", "toolkit/modules/ActorManagerParent.sys.mjs"], "git_node": "5010a018d0b1b99855784766cf6d2b79c57ade8c", "git_parents": ["21e00a1abeb89d6dfbeeb6cca0259f4d5a615cba"], "node": "f5540e7540dbcfa9cba191e41144ffa0c4574cfa", "parents": ["5ea175badcc0c6195ddb90c25ee9a19c70e5ba94"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Erik Nordin \u003cenordin@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010993 - Add TranslationsFeature Telemetry  a=dmeehan\n\nThis commit adds 3 new telemetry metrics so that we can tell how frequently\nthe Translatiosn feature is being enabled, disabled, or reset from the settings,\nespecially compared to how often the global AI switch is being flipped.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280542\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D281214\n", "files": ["toolkit/components/translations/TranslationsFeature.sys.mjs", "toolkit/components/translations/TranslationsTelemetry.sys.mjs", "toolkit/components/translations/metrics.yaml", "toolkit/components/translations/tests/browser/browser_translations_ai_feature.js", "toolkit/components/translations/tests/browser/shared-head.js"], "git_node": "e1e7b4f84cc2d774297e1280f41b1eec52cbf3ae", "git_parents": ["5010a018d0b1b99855784766cf6d2b79c57ade8c"], "node": "a7decd5c133764d35a77cba711239e0f4f3cde08", "parents": ["f5540e7540dbcfa9cba191e41144ffa0c4574cfa"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Erik Nordin \u003cenordin@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2010993 - Update Android Test Expectations  a=dmeehan\n\nThis commit ensures that the test expectations on Android\nreflect the new flow of the FullPage Translations language\nstate and detection logic.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D280872\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D281215\n", "files": ["mobile/android/geckoview/src/androidTest/java/org/mozilla/geckoview/test/TranslationsTest.kt", "toolkit/components/translations/actors/TranslationsParent.sys.mjs"], "git_node": "0debdb6d96808c4afc90d34354cf5b8eb68405e9", "git_parents": ["e1e7b4f84cc2d774297e1280f41b1eec52cbf3ae"]